---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Persona: The Developer | Admin</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; background: #030712; color: #f9fafb; }
    .header { background: #111827; border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2937; padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24, #d97706); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    .back-link { color: #9ca3af; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #374151; }
    .back-link:hover { color: #fbbf24; border-color: #fbbf24; }
    .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px; }
    .hero { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; padding: 24px; background: #111827; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-top: 3px solid #10b981; }
    .hero-icon { font-size: 56px; }
    .hero-name { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
    .hero-role { font-size: 13px; color: #10b981; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .section { background: #111827; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #fbbf24; margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .section p, .section li { font-size: 14px; color: #d1d5db; line-height: 1.7; }
    .section ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    .section li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; background: #064e3b; color: #6ee7b7; margin: 2px 4px 2px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">⚙️ xConvert24 Admin</div>
    <a href="/admin/personas" class="back-link">← All Personas</a>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-icon">🛠️</div>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-name">The Developer</div>
        <div class="hero-role">Widget Integrator</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">📋 Bio</div>
      <p>The Developer builds apps and websites that need conversion functionality. Rather than implementing their own conversion logic, they embed xConvert24 widgets or use the embed page to integrate unit conversion into their own products. They care about API reliability, documentation quality, and embed customisation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🎯 Goals</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Embed conversion widgets into their own applications</li>
        <li>Access reliable, well-documented embed endpoints</li>
        <li>Customise widget appearance to match their brand</li>
        <li>Ensure the embed is responsive and performant</li>
        <li>Get notified if the widget API changes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">😤 Pain Points</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Lack of comprehensive API documentation</li>
        <li>Widget styling conflicts with their existing CSS</li>
        <li>No versioned endpoints — breaking changes without warning</li>
        <li>Limited customisation options for embedded widgets</li>
        <li>No sandbox/testing environment</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🧭 Typical Journey</div>
      <p>Searches for "embeddable unit converter widget" → discovers /widgets page → tests a widget in iframe → checks /embed page for options → integrates into their app → monitors for any display issues.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">📊 Key Metrics</div>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Visit frequency:</strong> Monthly (for updates/docs)</li>
        <li><strong>Primary pages:</strong> /widgets, /embed, /tech-stack</li>
        <li><strong>Integration count:</strong> 1–3 widgets embedded</li>
        <li><strong>Support needs:</strong> Embed documentation, sizing guides</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🏷️ Tags</div>
      <span class="tag">Technical</span>
      <span class="tag">API Consumer</span>
      <span class="tag">Widget Embedder</span>
      <span class="tag">Documentation-driven</span>
      <span class="tag">Low Frequency</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
